description: A command line utility for installing and running analysis tools and processing and viewing their results.
releaseNotes:
## v0.69.1 - 4/21/2021
      - Task #48913: Microsoft.Guardian.Cli Release v0.69.1

      ### Fixed
      - Bug #47926: APIScanWrapper folder (in .gdn\.r) needs to be cleaned up by GDN  APIScan plugin
      - Bug #48429: Roslyn "autofill" option doesn't work well with pipelines running multiple build agents
      - Bug #48880: AptGetClient does not use CommandLineBuilder and thus has arguments with spaces issues
      - Bug #48884: AptGet package PeerDependencies can install PeerDependencies

      ### Added
      - Task #48544: Add BinSkim V1.8.0 prerelease3 (for internal) to GDN (and get the new package name, from new pkg source)
      - Task #48067: Add support for "Standard" logging which is available in APIScan v3.1.30022.8
      - Task #48653: Add gdntool for APIScan v3.1.30022.8, with addition for verbosity
      - Task #48855: Bumping version of M365 custom publisher to v0.5.0

      ### Changed
      - User Story #43125: Allow a gdnconfig to point to the latest version of a tool
